description: Nimbus Group AB manufactures leisure boats. The company is headquartered in Vaestra Froelunda, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 307 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2021-02-09. The firm is engaged in designing, manufacturing and marketing recreational boats. Nimbus Group includes seven brands - Alukin, Aquador, Bella, Falcon, Flipper, Nimbus and Paragon Yachts. The firm conducts sales in Europe and America.
name: Nimbus Group AB (publ)
